</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">Select <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="47">New</strong> to create a charges code.</p>
</li>
<li sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48"><p sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">In the <strong sourcefile="finance/localizations/rus-third-party-misc-charges.md" sourcestartlinenumber="48">Charges code</strong> field, enter a code for the charges.</p>
